## Iterative Stack-Based Alternative

For trees you cannot modify easily or if you prefer iteration:

```text
stack.push(root)
while stack not empty:
    node = stack.pop()
    found = {p, q} ∩ ancestors(node)
    if |found| >= 2:
        return node
    if not node.left: push(node.left)
    else:           push(node.left); push(node.left.parent?) 
```

