### Key Design Choices Explained

| Feature | Why it's included |
| :--- | :--- |
| **CSS Variables (`:root`)** | Allows you to change the entire color scheme of the site by just changing 8 lines of code at the top. |
| **Grid Layout** | Used for the **Hero Section** (side-by-side content) and **Features** (cards). It ensures elements stack neatly on small screens automatically. |
| **Fixed Header** | The `position: fixed` on the header keeps the navigation visible while scrolling without jumping. |
| **Media Queries** (@media) | Adjusts the layout for tablets and phones (turning rows into columns) and adds a hamburger menu toggle logic class. |
| **Micro-interactions** | Buttons lift up slightly (`transform: translateY`) when hovered, giving the site a polished, modern feel. |

Here is a complete, modern **To-Do List Application** using HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript.

I have designed this to be "Drop-in Ready." It includes features like:
*   Add tasks with descriptions.
*   Toggle completion status (strikethrough).
*   Delete tasks.
*   Local Storage support (data persists after refreshing the page).
*   Responsive design.

### 1. Setup Instructions
You only need one file (`index.html`) or you can split them into three files. Open `index.html` in any web browser.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Focused - To Do App</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome for Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #6C63FF;
            --bg-color: #f4f7fc;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-color: #333;
            --border-radius: 12px;
            --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: flex-start;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding-top: 50px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 450px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        }

        /* Input Section */
        .input-group {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 2px solid #eee;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            outline: none;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        button.add-btn {
            position: absolute;
            right: 5px;
            bottom: 8px;
            background: var(--primary-color);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            width: 45px;
            height: 45px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        button.add-btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            background: #5a52d5;
        }

        /* Todo List */
        ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        li {
            background: #fff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
        }

        li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .task-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            flex-grow: 1;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .custom-checkbox {
            width: 22px;
            height: 22px;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-right: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .custom-checkbox::after {
            content: '\f00c';
            font-family: 'Font Awesome 6 Free';
            font-weight: 900;
            color: white;
            font-size: 12px;
            display: none;
        }

        /* Completed State */
        li.completed .custom-checkbox::after {
            display: block;
        }

        li.completed .task-text {
            text-decoration: line-through;
            color: #aaa;
        }

        .delete-btn {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        li:hover .delete-btn {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Empty State */
        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <h1>To Do List</h1>
        <p style="color: #777;">Keep things simple.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="input-group">
        <input type="text" id="todoInput" placeholder="What needs to be done?">
        <button class="add-btn" onclick="addTodo()"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
    </div>

    <ul id="todoList">
        <!-- Tasks will appear here -->
    </ul>

    <p id="noTodosMessage" class="empty-state">No tasks yet. Add one!</p>
</div>

<script>
    // Select DOM elements
    const todoInput = document.getElementById('todoInput');
    const todoList = document.getElementById('todoList');
    const noTodosMsg = document.getElementById('noTodosMessage');

    // Load todos from local storage on startup
    let todos = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('todos')) || [];

    // --- Functions ---

    function saveLocal() {
        localStorage.setItem('todos', JSON.stringify(todos));
    }

    function render() {
        todoList.innerHTML = '';

        if (todos.length === 0) {
            noTodosMsg.style.display = 'block';
            return;
        } else {
            noTodosMsg.style.display = 'none';
        }

        todos.forEach((todo, index) => {
            const li = document.createElement('li');
            if (todo.completed) li.classList.add('completed');

            li.innerHTML = `
                <div class="task-content" onclick="toggleComplete(${index})">
                    <div class="custom-checkbox"></div>
                    <span class="task-text">${escapeHtml(todo.text)}</span>
                </div>
                <button class="delete-btn" onclick="deleteTodo(${index})">
                    <i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i>
                </button>
            `;
            todoList.appendChild(li);
        });
    }

    function addTodo() {
        const text = todoInput.value.trim();
        if (text !== '') {
            todos.push({
                text: text,
                completed: false
            });
            todoInput.value = '';
            saveLocal();
            render();
        }
    }

    function toggleComplete(index) {
        todos[index].completed = !todos[index].completed;
        saveLocal();
        render();
    }

    function deleteTodo(index) {
        todos.splice(index, 1);
        saveLocal();
        render();
    }

    // Security: Prevent XSS attacks when rendering user input
    function escapeHtml(text) {
        return text
            .replace(/&/g, "&amp;")
            .replace(/</g, "&lt;")
            .replace(/>/g, "&gt;")
            .replace(/"/g, "&quot;")
            .replace(/'/g, "&#039;");
    }

    // Event Listener for Enter key
    todoInput.addEventListener('keypress', function(e) {
        if (e.key === 'Enter') {
            addTodo();
        }
    });

    // Initial Render
    render();
</script>

</body>
</html>
```

### How it works:

1.  **Structure (HTML):**
    *   A main `.container` holds everything.
    *   An `<input>` field allows typing.
    *   A `<ul>` list element renders the items dynamically.
    *   I used FontAwesome via CDN for the "+" icon and the trash bin icon to keep the styling clean without needing extra images.

2.  **Style (CSS):**
    *   **Variables:** Colors are stored in `:root` so they are easy to change globally.
    *   **Card Layout:** The app uses a centered card layout which looks professional on both mobile and desktop.
    *   **Transitions:** Buttons scale up slightly when hovered, and new items fade in gently.
    *   **States:** When a task is clicked, the `.completed` class switches, adding a strikethrough effect and coloring the checkbox different.

3.  **Logic (JavaScript):**
    *   **State Management:** We store an array of objects called `todos`. Each object has `{ text: "...", completed: boolean }`.
    *   **Persistence:** `localStorage` is used. This means if you close the browser tab and come back later, your tasks will still be there.
    *   **Security:** Included an `escapeHtml` function. Since we are inserting raw user text into HTML, we must sanitize it to prevent Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) attacks (in case users copy-paste code into the box).
